  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2335287588" />
    <a title="Derek Wolfgram" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1219345-derek-wolfgram"><img alt="Derek Wolfgram" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1212790404p2/1219345.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2335287588?book_show_action=true">Apr 08, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Derek Wolfgram" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Derek Wolfgram" href="/user/show/1219345-derek-wolfgram">Derek Wolfgram</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2335287588" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8341017595186762264">Palahniuk&apos;s best book since Lullaby. While the narrative is a bit jumbled, the paranoid libertarian fantasy world in the story is a brilliant extrapolation of today&apos;s political environment, and could only have been written by the author of Fight Club. Darkly funny and poignant.</span>
  <span id="freeText8341017595186762264" style="display:none">Palahniuk's best book since Lullaby. While the narrative is a bit jumbled, the paranoid libertarian fantasy world in the story is a brilliant extrapolation of today's political environment, and could only have been written by the author of Fight Club. Darkly funny and poignant.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8341017595186762264" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

