      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/58031436-adjustment-day">Quotes from Adjustment Day</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Hoard food and it rots. Hoard money and you rot. Hoard power and the nation rots.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/9296979-hoard-food-and-it-rots-hoard-money-and-you-rot">11 likes</a>
            </nobr>
